title: Daniel Jones dominates in debut, NFL Preseason Week 1, Breakout defenses (Football 8/9)
description:
Will Brinson, John Breech and Ryan Wilson rock out in a jam packed podcast episode for the first week of the NFL season, looking at the debut for Daniel Jones (2:45), as well as Dwayne Haskins (14:50), the Duke Johnson trade (17:30), Josh Rosen playing under pressure (22:00), David Singletary looking sharp (26:15), Ron Rivera icing kickers (28:00), Kyler Murray's debut (30:00), Melvin Gordon losing the Chargers game (35:00), Jakobi Meyers dominating (37:30), Joe Webb!! (43:00), Titans QB drama (44:00), Nate Sudfeld's injury (45:10), John Harbaugh ATS (48:15) and much more. Then the guys take a look at the best possible breakout defenses for 2019.
